https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>上周在社交媒体上发表了极大的争议，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>被他的人才代理机构（Talent Agency）放弃了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据一份<a href="https://variety.com/2025/music/news/kanye-west-dropped-talent-agency-antisemitic-behavior-1236304073/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>综艺</em></a>报道，西部（现在是法律称为Ye）在星期一（2月10日）被他的代理机构，总部位于洛杉矶的33＆West抛弃。在33＆West，坎耶（Kanye）由特工丹尼尔·麦卡特尼（Daniel McCartney）代表，他曾在社交媒体上宣布他和该机构将与说唱歌手断开所有联系。</p><p>根据<em>Variety</em>的报道，麦卡特尼在一个现已具备的Instagram故事中写道，33＆West正在抛弃Kanye“立即有效”，并解释说这是因为“由于他的有害和可恶的言论，我本人Nor 33＆West可以代表。” </p><figure id="attachment_3782073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782073" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特。学分：哥谭/GC图像" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782073" class="wp-caption-text">