-kanye-west@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-drake-kanye-west@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一个由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ai">AI</a>创建的Deepfake视频，讲述了几种流行文化人物，其中包括“ Fuck Kanye” T恤，以抗议说唱歌手最近有争议的社交媒体帖子。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</a></strong></li></ul><p>在过去的两个星期中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a> （现在是合法的，已经有了YE），​​这引起了前所未有的争议。上周，坎耶（Kanye） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-kanye-west-shows-up-with-wife-bianca-censori-who-reveals-shocking-see-through-dress-3833867">和他的妻子比安卡·康塞里（Bianca Censori）一起参加了格莱美奖（Grammys Red Carpet），后者穿着透明的连衣裙，露出了她的裸体身材</a>。</p><p>此后，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reveals-he-has-autism-and-was-misdiagnosed-with-bipolar-disorder-3835269">在一次采访中透露他患有自闭症，并认为他在2016年被双相情感障碍误诊</a>。他还分享说，他已经停止服用双相情感障碍药物。</p><p>然后，他通过表达了对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">迪迪</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-brown">克里斯·布朗的支持，返回X（以前是Twitter），</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">敦促在性虐待指控中被释放出狱</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3836540" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836540" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836540" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca.jpg" alt="Kanye West和Bianca Censori" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-kanye-bianca-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836540" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）和比安卡·辛森（Bianca Censori）在2024年图片。信贷：Swan Gallet/WWD通过Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>随着他开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">对妻子Censori宣称“统治”</a> ，并大声疾呼<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">向犹太社区撤回他的道歉</a>，并宣称自己是“纳粹”和A其他贬低的帖子针对几个社区。</p><p>在周一超级碗之后，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）指导追随者到他的网站，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">一件出售的物品 - 一件白色T恤，胸部上列为“ HH-01”，胸部上有一个大的swastika</a> 。这件衣服的价格为20美元，上市的名称为“ HH-01”，可能是对纳粹手势的“ Heil Hitler” Chant的引用。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">此后，该网站已被取消</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">坎耶（Kanye）的X帐户已被停用</a>。</p><p>为了抗议Swastika Tee及其对犹太社区的评论，在社交媒体上分享了一个新的Deepfake AI视频，标题“足够了”。 The viral clip features the likeness of Mark Zuckerberg, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scarlett-johansson">Scarlett Johansson</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mila-kunis">Drake</a> , David Schwimmer, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jerry-seinfeld">Jerry Seinfeld</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ben-stiller">Ben Stiller</a> and more sporting a white t-shirt with the Star of David in the middle of a middle finger emblem and Kanye&#39;s name written beneath it 。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “足够了。” </p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f595.png" alt="🖕" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />坎耶·韦斯特。</p><p>使这个病毒。 <a href="https://t.co/eqCmQNksn2">pic.twitter.com/eqCmQNksn2</a></p><p> — Vivid. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1ee-1f1f1.png" alt="🇮🇱" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> (@VividProwess) <a href="https://twitter.com/VividProwess/status/1889406552903393660?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 11, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Later on in the video, more stars are revealed, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adam-sandler">Adam Sandler</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mila-kunis">Mila Kunis</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-black">Jack Black</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/natalie-portman">Natalie Portman</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steven-spielberg">Steven Spielberg</a> and more, with Sandler flipping off the camera, seemingly directed at Kanye West.</p><p> At the time of writing, none of the celebrities whose likeness was used in the AI video have reacted to the viral clip.</p><p> American singer-songwriter, DJ and producer Matthew Koma took to his official Instagram account to share that he has made a <a href="https://shop.wbleague.com/products/fkw-tee?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaYeVWzZ-c9ofI9b0jRgWjWpTWVCoSVRDN4xaWz1gKJTANhgqyiIpy32_pg_aem_7X9E9pdM0yJNrhl_wHW6Ww" target="_blank" rel="noopener">t-shirt</a> with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">the phrase “Fuck Ye” on the chest</a> . “嘿，我也可以制作一件衬衫 - 链接在Bio中，所有收益都将用于蓝卡大屠杀幸存者慈善机构，”阅读该帖子的标题。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Charlie-Puth">查理·普斯（Charlie Puth）</a>还通过Instagram故事分享了一条信息， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">恳求他停止推广“极为危险”的信息</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><i>朋友</i></a>明星戴维·施温默（David Schwimmer）以前还曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">呼吁采取行动对说唱歌手</a>，因为他充满仇恨的“纳粹”帖子，认为“沉默是同谋”。</p><p> In other news, Ye recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-kendrick-lamars-halftime-show-is-his-favourite-since-michael-jacksons-3836803">revealed that he&#39;s a fan of Kendrick Lamar&#39;s recent Super Bowl Halftime Show</a> , calling it his “favourite” since <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Michael-Jackson">Michael Jackson</a> &#39;s iconic 1993 performance.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deepfake-ai-video-featuring-mark-zuckerberg-drake-david-schwimmer-and-more-wearing-fuck-kanye-shirt-goes-viral-3837229">Deepfake AI video featuring Mark Zuckerberg, Drake, David Schwi